-----------
mkinitramfs
-----------

This is an initramfs creator for Sulin, Mkinitramfs part is written in Python,
the init script running in boot process is written as shell script (ash compatible).

Init script creates a temporary initramfs to do initial system booting tasks
(storage probing, graphic card initialization) for installed systems and live
systems. It can also be used as a very basic rescue system for failsafe operations.


For initramfs options, see the output of

mkinitramfs --help
